videos.description: Trae Young gets Oklahoma out in front early with a deep 3-pointer against TCU.
videos.headline: Young launches deep 3 for Sooners

videos.description: TCU's Ahmed Hamdy-Mohamed backs down a defender for a hook shot to finish a 10-0 run for the Horned Frogs.
videos.headline: Hamdy-Mohamed knocks down hook shot to cap 10-point run

videos.description: Trae Young finds Kameron McGusty in transition who converts the and-1 layup.
videos.headline: OU's McGusty goes up strong for and-1

videos.description: Trae Young gets the Sooners back out in front with a 3 quickly followed by a technical foul for TCU head coach Jamie Dixon.
videos.headline: Young hits 3, TCU coach gets tech

videos.description: Trae Young shows off his range by hitting a 3-pointer from the TCU logo.
videos.headline: Young pulls up from logo for 3

videos.description: Oklahoma's Rashard Odomes cuts to the hoop and extends for the basket, drawing a foul.
videos.headline: Odomes leaps and reaches for hoop

videos.description: Desmond Bane gets out in front on the fastbreak for a big dunk.
videos.headline: Bane hammers dunk for TCU

videos.description: Jamuni McNeace elevates for a huge dunk off a pass from Trae Young.
videos.headline: McNeace throws down for Oklahoma

videos.description: Trae Young crosses over and pulls up from deep to keep Oklahoma close to TCU.
videos.headline: Young pulls up for fifth 3-pointer

videos.description: Trae Young fires a bounce pass to Kameron McGusty, who gets the bucket on basket interference by TCU.
videos.headline: Young threads needle on pass to McGusty

videos.description: Trae Young finds Kameron McGusty in transition who pulls up for a 3 to tie the game at 83.
videos.headline: McGusty ties it with corner 3

videos.description: Kameron McGusty gets open off an offensive rebound to hit a clutch 3 to put Oklahoma up 88-87.
videos.headline: McGusty's late 3 gives OU lead

videos.description: Oklahoma's Trae Young explains how he stays focused with lofty ambitions on him while playing for the Sooners.
videos.headline: Young: 'I came here to win a championship'

videos.description: Oklahoma freshman Trae Young nets a historic 39 points and 14 assists to lead the Sooners to a comeback win over TCU.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Highlight (Historic effort by Young in comeback win) 2017/12/30 ODV ENHL

videos.headline: Historic effort by Young in comeback win
